content: tcm390: Merged 8 pull requests in the elizaos/eliza repository, contributing a mix of bug fixes and features totaling +8468/-1585 lines of code. The most significant change was elizaos/eliza#5248, which added a background color to dialog content (+5415/-561 lines). They also opened one new pull request (elizaos/eliza#5261) during a moderately consistent week of activity.
